 jako ponojdonirali.

585
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:17,440
 Mogu reći negdje

586
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:20,280
 da smo stavili u prodaju

587
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,780
 a polo, dakle, smo

588
00:37:21,780 --> 00:37:23,360
 radili donaciju

589
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:24,720
 i to nam je omogućilo

590
00:37:24,720 --> 00:37:26,800
 da ne moramo dati otkaze

591
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:28,140
 i da možemo

592
00:37:28,140 --> 00:37:30,060
 isplaćivati uredno plaće

593
00:37:30,060 --> 00:37:31,080
 našim ljudima.

594
00:37:31,080 --> 00:37:32,340
 Naravno, sad smo

595
00:37:32,340 --> 00:37:34,260
 kako je to sve nekako

596
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:36,040
 reći stabiliziralo

597
00:37:36,040 --> 00:37:37,120
 u našoj branši.

598
00:37:37,120 --> 00:37:38,280
 Nastavili smo mi

599
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:39,840
 proizvoditi naše proizvode

600
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:41,140
 i čak mogu reći

601
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:42,240
 da širimo se.

602
00:37:42,240 --> 00:37:44,180
 Nije nas to nešto sad

603
00:37:44,180 --> 00:37:46,280
 ugrozilo, ali smo uspjeli

604
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:48,180
 u tom nekom kriznom trenutku

605
00:37:48,180 --> 00:37:50,040
 izvući ono najbolje.

606
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:54,420
 Uvijek volimo čuti ovako

607
00:37:54,420 --> 00:37:56,100
 dobre, ljepe priče,

608
00:37:56,100 --> 00:37:58,320
 pozitivne, poduzetničke priče.

609
00:37:58,320 --> 00:38:00,920
 To nekako u ovoj situaciji

610
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:02,120
 u kojoj je puno loših vijesti

611
00:38:02,120 --> 00:38:04,320
 uvijek je lijepo čuti nešto

612
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,000
 pozitivno.

613
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:07,040
 Slavica, ti se baviš

614
00:38:07,040 --> 00:38:10,080
 branšom koja je jedna

615
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:11,780
 od najpogođenijih

616
00:38:11,780 --> 00:38:14,080
 u ovoj COVID-19 krizi.

617
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:16,000
 Kako si se ti snašla?

618
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:19,160
 Pa ne znam baš još uvijek

619
00:38:19,160 --> 00:38:20,240
 ja sam li se snašla.

620
00:38:20,240 --> 00:38:22,000
 Mi smo prošle godine...

621
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:23,500
 Snalaziš se!

622
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:28,880
 Snalaziš se polako.

623
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:30,660
 Snalazim se, da.

624
00:38:30,660 --> 00:38:32,840
 Nama je, što je Stjepan rekao,

625
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:35,080
 isključivo ovisimo potraženje,

626
00:38:35,080 --> 00:38:36,640
 koja je apsolutno zaustavljena.

627
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:38,000
 Mi smo se pripremili

628
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:39,540
 za ovu godinu,

629
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:40,880
 potencijalno ako se dogodi.

630
00:38:42,620 --> 00:38:44,160
 i pripremili smo nešto

631
00:38:44,160 --> 00:38:45,560
 što će se tražiti sad

632
00:38:45,560 --> 00:38:46,400
 u ovim vremenima

633
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:47,320
 koja dolaze

634
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:49,940
 i tiče se i sigurnostnih protokola

635
00:38:49,940 --> 00:38:50,620
 i opće načina

636
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:51,460
 dolazka gostju

637
00:38:51,460 --> 00:38:53,020
 i sve ostalo.

638
00:38:53,020 --> 00:38:54,140
 Tako da, ako krene,

639
00:38:54,140 --> 00:38:54,960
 mi smo spremni.

640
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,680
 I nadamo se da će krenuti

641
00:38:56,680 --> 00:38:58,120
 kroz neka 3-4 mjesece.

642
00:38:58,220 --> 00:38:59,240
 ne znam koliko ćemo moći

643
00:38:59,240 --> 00:39:00,080
 dugo još ovako.

644
00:39:00,080 --> 00:39:02,100
 Jer, mislim,

645
00:39:02,100 --> 00:39:03,420
 svi smo se stavili

646
00:39:03,420 --> 00:39:05,000
 apsolutno odmah

647
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:06,580
 i okupili ono najbolje

648
00:39:06,580 --> 00:39:08,140
 što imamo tu u našoj Županiji.

649
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:10,060
 I svi smo nekako skupa

650
00:39:10,060 --> 00:39:12,620
 pokušali napraviti neku promjenu

651
00:39:12,620 --> 00:39:13,780
 jer Dubrovnik je stvarno

652
00:39:13,780 --> 00:39:15,000
 najviše pogođen.

653
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,920
 Mi smo stvarili 10% prometa

654
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:18,040
 od 2019.

655
00:39:18,040 --> 00:39:20,520
 Tako da će se puno, puno stvari

656
00:39:20,520 --> 00:39:21,540
 promijeniti u ovaj godinu.

657
00:39:21,540 --> 00:39:27,760
 Da, da, puno će se toga promijeniti.

658
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:30,060
 puno toga se već i promijenilo.

659
00:39:30,060 --> 00:39:32,820
 Svakako, biće zanimljivo vidjeti

660
00:39:32,820 --> 00:39:36,080
 kako će ova godina dalje ići.

661
00:39:36,080 --> 00:39:37,680
 A sad smo nekako prošli

662
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:38,720
 i glavne probleme

663
00:39:38,720 --> 00:39:41,860
 s kojima se žene, poduzetnice susreću

664
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:44,680
 i nekakva potencijalna rješenja

665
00:39:44,680 --> 00:39:45,340
 tih problema.

666
00:39:45,340 --> 00:39:47,420
 Ali, bližimo se kraju.

667
00:39:47,420 --> 00:39:48,680
 Pa ajmo nekako sumirati.

668
00:39:48,680 --> 00:39:50,920
 Rekli smo, htjeli bismo privući

669
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:53,760
 još žena da se bave poduzetništvom,

670
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:55,820
 da se otisnu na to putovanje.

671
00:39:55,820 --> 00:39:57,500
 Ali, zašto bi,

672
00:39:57,540 --> 00:39:58,580
 za našu društvo,

673
00:39:58,580 --> 00:40:00,040
 zašto bi za Hrvatsku

674
00:40:00,040 --> 00:40:02,620
 bilo dobro da bude što više

675
00:40:02,620 --> 00:40:04,040
 žena poduzetnica.

676
00:40:04,040 --> 00:40:05,860
 Ivana, što ti kažeš?

677
00:40:05,860 --> 00:40:09,160
 Pa ja, justo kad idem

678
00:40:09,160 --> 00:40:11,160
 po tim gradovima i selima,

679
00:40:11,160 --> 00:40:14,100
 onda pričam da su zapravo,

680
00:40:14,100 --> 00:40:15,880
 da bi poduzetnice se trebalo držati

681
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:17,840
 kao malo vode na dlanu.

682
00:40:17,840 --> 00:40:23,080
 jer ipak svako ko pokene biznis je kreirao barem sebi radno mjesto,

683
00:40:23,080 --> 00:40:24,600
 jedno novo dodatno,

684
00:40:24,600 --> 00:40:29,280
 plus sve ova radna mjesta ljudi koje će zaposliti.

685
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:31,740
 Dakle, to je jedna stvar.

686
00:40:32,300 --> 00:40:35,100
 a druga stvar je demografsko pitanje.

687
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:38,100
 I poduzetnice, dakle,

688
00:40:38,100 --> 00:40:39,520
 imaju i djecu,

689
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:41,300
 tako da mislim da ne moram

690
00:40:41,300 --> 00:40:44,660
 ništa dolazno objašnjavati.

691
00:40:45,300 --> 00:40:47,180
 I to je, dakle,

692
00:40:47,180 --> 00:40:49,800
 osobito važno za ove žene,

693
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,580
 za ove državu poput naše,

694
00:40:51,580 --> 00:40:53,040
 koja je na koljenima.

695
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:56,080
 Često puta netko me pitao

696
00:40:56,080 --> 00:40:58,900
 šta Njemačka radi po tom pitanju.

697
00:40:58,900 --> 00:41:00,920
 Pa Njemačka ne radi puno

698
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:03,120
 zato što ima puno više stranika.

699
00:41:03,120 --> 00:41:06,180
 Bogati su to vam isto kao da imate, ne znam,

700
00:41:06,180 --> 00:41:06,940
 Lamborghini,

701
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:08,760
 imate, ne znam,

702
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:10,540
 onaj Bentley, jel tako?

703
00:41:10,540 --> 00:41:11,440
 I sad vas neko pita,

704
00:41:11,440 --> 00:41:12,080
 ovo ćeš Tesla?

705
00:41:12,080 --> 00:41:13,180
 Pa naj, dobro, može,

706
00:41:13,180 --> 00:41:15,280
 ali nije sad neka nužda, jel tako?

707
00:41:16,080 --> 00:41:18,620
 Kao što je kod nas trenutno nužda

708
00:41:18,620 --> 00:41:20,520
 i ekonomska i demografska

709
00:41:20,520 --> 00:41:23,540
 i upravo zato su važne žene poduzetnice.

710
00:41:23,540 --> 00:41:25,660
 Evo, Stjepan je lijepo elaborirao

711
00:41:25,660 --> 00:41:27,220
 svoje istraživanje,

712
00:41:27,220 --> 00:41:31,500
 koliko je taj povrat

713
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:33,460
 na investiciju žene,

714
00:41:33,460 --> 00:41:35,680
 tako da mislim da su to

715
00:41:35,680 --> 00:41:38,000
 dobre lekcije za naše političare.

716
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:41,660
 Stjepan, evo, imaš li još ti nešto dodati?

717
00:41:41,660 --> 00:41:44,260
 Zašto su važne žene poduzetnice?

718
00:41:44,620 --> 00:41:45,680
 Paziš što hoćeš reći,

719
00:41:45,680 --> 00:41:46,780
 tu si među ženama,

720
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:49,840
 tako da delikatne situacija.

721
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:51,780
 Mi kažemo,

722
00:41:51,780 --> 00:41:53,020
 ekonomija postoji pozitivna

723
00:41:53,020 --> 00:41:54,380
 i normativna ekonomska analiza.

724
00:41:54,380 --> 00:41:55,780
 Pozitivna je ovo s brojima,

725
00:41:55,780 --> 00:41:56,800
 kad imate nešto konkretno,

726
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:57,380
 normativna,

727
00:41:57,380 --> 00:41:59,000
 kako bi društvo trebalo izgledati

728
00:41:59,000 --> 00:41:59,800
 u budućnosti.

729
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,420
 I sad tu, naravno,

730
00:42:01,420 --> 00:42:02,480
 se treba prvo složiti,

731
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:03,060
 što je cilj?

732
00:42:03,060 --> 00:42:05,160
 Je li cilj veća jednakost,

733
00:42:05,160 --> 00:42:06,500
 je li cilj ekonomski rast?

734
00:42:06,500 --> 00:42:08,320
 Ako je cilj primjerica ekonomski rast,

735
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:09,460
 želiš da najbolji ljudi

736
00:42:09,460 --> 00:42:12,600
 rade na poslove koje bi trebali raditi.

737
00:42:12,600 --> 00:42:16,020
 Ono što ja mogu reći svakako

738
00:42:16,020 --> 00:42:18,020
 je da bi poticanje ženskog potica,

739
00:42:18,020 --> 00:42:19,520
 što je trebalo krenuti u doslovnoj školi.

740
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:22,420
 I to bi trebalo postepeno ugraditi,

741
00:42:22,420 --> 00:42:23,120
 jer što su škole?

742
00:42:23,120 --> 00:42:23,760
 Škola nije ništa.

743
00:42:23,760 --> 00:42:25,180
 Mislim, kada bi ovako grubo rekli,

744
00:42:25,180 --> 00:42:26,880
 to je tvornica ljudi,

745
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:28,020
 tu prolazimo svi,

746
00:42:28,020 --> 00:42:29,400
 mi smo prošli kroz školu

747
00:42:29,400 --> 00:42:30,680
 i dobili smo nešto

748
00:42:30,680 --> 00:42:32,660
 u naše razmišljene.

749
00:42:32,660 --> 00:42:34,040
 Pa tako bi trebalo poticati

750
00:42:34,040 --> 00:42:35,980
 taj podvrdički način razmišljena.

751
00:42:35,980 --> 00:42:36,600
 Što se tiče

752
00:42:36,600 --> 00:42:38,920
 i nekih potpora u kratkom roku.

753
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:39,860
 Dakle,

754
00:42:39,860 --> 00:42:42,960
 ovaj primjer potpora što smo radili,

755
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:43,600
 znači,

756
00:42:43,600 --> 00:42:45,460
 ne kažem da bi trebalo napreti

757
00:42:45,460 --> 00:42:47,400
 identičnu takvu šemu,

758
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:47,680
 znači,

759
00:42:47,680 --> 00:42:48,680
 može se toliko uboljšati,

760
00:42:48,680 --> 00:42:49,900
 sigurno se može uboljšati,

761
00:42:49,900 --> 00:42:51,640
 ali to je jedan dobar primjer

762
00:42:51,640 --> 00:42:52,520
 koji je ukinut.

763
00:42:52,520 --> 00:42:53,260
 Dakle,

764
00:42:53,260 --> 00:42:53,940
 to su bile žene,

765
00:42:53,940 --> 00:42:55,860
 taj potpora šema žene podvrdički

766
00:42:55,860 --> 00:42:57,280
 koje je vodilo ministarstvo,

767
00:42:57,280 --> 00:42:58,700
 podvrdično i obrata s njim,

768
00:42:58,700 --> 00:43:00,200
 je ukinuto.

769
00:43:00,200 --> 00:43:00,760
 Dakle,

770
00:43:00,760 --> 00:43:02,720
 postoje nekakve lokalne inicijative,

771
00:43:02,720 --> 00:43:05,500
 ali koliko je meni znano,

772
00:43:05,500 --> 00:43:06,900
 više ne postoje nacionalne razine.

773
00:43:06,900 --> 00:43:07,580
 Dakle,

774
00:43:07,580 --> 00:43:10,340
 tako nešto bi trebalo postojati,

775
00:43:10,340 --> 00:43:12,060
 jer žene imaju to ograničenje,

776
00:43:12,060 --> 00:43:13,560
 nastavno muškaraca glede vremena,

777
00:43:13,560 --> 00:43:15,060
 što se pričaju zbog djece,

778
00:43:15,060 --> 00:43:18,000
 a postoji ta nekakva psikološka literatura

779
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:19,660
 koja kaže da su žene opreznije

780
00:43:19,660 --> 00:43:22,160
 kad ulaze u podvrdični poduhvat

781
00:43:22,160 --> 00:43:24,460
 i s te strane mi potreba možda nekakav savjet.

782
00:43:24,540 --> 00:43:27,540
 I mislim da je to apsolutno dobra mjera

783
00:43:27,540 --> 00:43:29,160
 i da bi se to trebalo poticati,

784
00:43:29,160 --> 00:43:30,540
 a dalje potpore,

785
00:43:30,540 --> 00:43:32,460
 dovoljimo ovim velikim iznosima,

786
00:43:32,460 --> 00:43:34,060
 bi trebali po mojoj mišljenju

787
00:43:34,060 --> 00:43:36,480
 biti isključivo temeljem slučnosti.

788
00:43:36,480 --> 00:43:38,120
 Ali naravno,

789
00:43:38,120 --> 00:43:39,480
 što je imala spomeno,

790
00:43:39,480 --> 00:43:39,740
 dakle,

791
00:43:39,740 --> 00:43:42,480
 taj problem vremena,

792
00:43:42,480 --> 00:43:43,180
 dakle,

793
00:43:43,180 --> 00:43:46,080
 tu bi se moglo pomoći ženama

794
00:43:46,080 --> 00:43:47,900
 i ono možda postoji,

795
00:43:47,900 --> 00:43:48,200
 ne znam,

796
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:49,800
 tisuću žena

797
00:43:49,800 --> 00:43:51,780
 koje bi bile fantasije žene poduznice,

798
00:43:51,780 --> 00:43:53,000
 ali nisu nikad dobile priliku.

799
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:54,860
 I to je onda nama trošak za duštvo.

800
00:43:54,860 --> 00:43:56,120
 Koliki to ne mogu reći,

801
00:43:56,120 --> 00:43:57,240
 nema nekakvog istraživanja.

802
00:43:57,240 --> 00:43:59,440
 Ali potencijalno postoji među ženama

803
00:43:59,440 --> 00:44:01,540
 neke žene koje danas rade,

804
00:44:01,540 --> 00:44:02,700
 možda ne znam kakav posao,

805
00:44:02,780 --> 00:44:04,800
 mogli su biti kožda fantasije žene poduznice.

806
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:07,780
 Tako da ovaj...

807
00:44:07,780 --> 00:44:11,940
 Trebamo ekonomski raz.

808
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:16,880
 Mislim da se svi slažemo u tome

809
00:44:16,880 --> 00:44:17,360
 i naravno,

810
00:44:17,360 --> 00:44:20,960
 nitko od žena ne traži nešto što im ne pripada,

811
00:44:20,960 --> 00:44:24,780
 nego samo jednaku startnu poziciju.

812
00:44:24,780 --> 00:44:28,220
 To naprosto malo više pomoći u početku

813
00:44:28,220 --> 00:44:31,340
 da budu doista žene jednake muškacima.

814
00:44:31,460 --> 00:44:35,280
 To je nešto prema čemu, nadam se, idemo.

815
00:44:35,280 --> 00:44:38,540
 A što se tiče ženskog poduzetništva

816
00:44:38,540 --> 00:44:40,520
 i mi udruzi glas poduzetnika

817
00:44:40,520 --> 00:44:42,320
 imamo odbor za žensko poduzetništvo

818
00:44:42,320 --> 00:44:43,260
 koje vodi Ivana.

819
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:47,420
 Stjepan je ti si član našeg ekonomskog savjeta.

820
00:44:47,420 --> 00:44:49,980
 Pa evo, možda je to dobra podloga

821
00:44:49,980 --> 00:44:51,860
 za jedno buduće istraživanje

822
00:44:51,860 --> 00:44:53,500
 o ženskom poduzetništvu.

823
00:44:53,500 --> 00:44:56,860
 Mi ćemo njači njegak u svoj odbor priključiti sad.

824
00:44:56,860 --> 00:45:00,520
 Ja nisam slučaj za žensko poduzetništvo.

825
00:45:00,600 --> 00:45:01,680
 Ja se bavim ekonomski tema.

826
00:45:01,680 --> 00:45:03,440
 Ovo je bilo nama ekonomski zanimljivo

827
00:45:03,440 --> 00:45:05,620
 jer postoji sad ta nova literatura

828
00:45:05,620 --> 00:45:07,840
 vezana za žene poduzetnice i za žene

829
00:45:07,840 --> 00:45:09,440
 općenito kako se ponašaju.

830
00:45:09,440 --> 00:45:11,920
 Tako da ja sam više vako generalni ekonomist.

831
00:45:12,780 --> 00:45:14,520
 To je baš ono što nam treba.

832
00:45:14,520 --> 00:45:15,160
 Dobro, ne?

833
00:45:15,160 --> 00:45:23,120
 Lagano smo se približili kraju.

834
00:45:23,120 --> 00:45:26,900
 Nadam se da vam je svima bio ugodan razgovor.

835
00:45:26,900 --> 00:45:30,180
 Nadam se i našim dragim slušateljima i gledateljima

836
00:45:30,180 --> 00:45:31,100
 da je bilo ugodno.

837
00:45:31,100 --> 00:45:35,140
 Evo, voljela bi još za kraj jednu misa o nešto

838
00:45:35,140 --> 00:45:38,520
 o šim možemo završiti da ostane među svim.

839
00:45:38,520 --> 00:45:40,560
 Evo, pogotovo damama koje nas gledaju,

840
00:45:40,560 --> 00:45:44,060
 a i muškarcima možda da malo bolje razumiju

841
00:45:44,060 --> 00:45:46,860
 i budu podpora svojim boljim polovicama

842
00:45:46,860 --> 00:45:49,120
 koje se žele opušati u poduzetništvu.

843
00:45:49,220 --> 00:45:49,800
 Evo, Ivana.

844
00:45:49,800 --> 00:45:55,260
 Pa evo, ja nekako sam naučila u svojih

845
00:45:55,260 --> 00:45:57,500
 koliko već devet godina poduzetništva

846
00:45:57,500 --> 00:45:59,360
 da uvijek se nekako,

847
00:45:59,360 --> 00:46:01,240
 situacija nam je stvarno grozna.

848
00:46:01,240 --> 00:46:03,820
 Mi evo u vimani nadvija svaki dan čekamo

849
00:46:03,820 --> 00:46:06,740
 na evo kad će krenuti otvaranje

850
00:46:06,740 --> 00:46:09,080
 jer mi ipak imamo jako puno i venata

851
00:46:09,080 --> 00:46:10,520
 i u njima smo ovisni.

852
00:46:10,520 --> 00:46:16,000
 Ali kažem, nekako, uvijek ti je trenutna situacija najteža.

853
00:46:16,000 --> 00:46:18,760
 Uvijek misliš da ne može gore,

854
00:46:18,920 --> 00:46:22,640
 ali onda uvijek se sve to nekako riješi.

855
00:46:22,640 --> 00:46:25,600
 Vidjeli smo da moramo čuvati mir

856
00:46:25,600 --> 00:46:27,080
 i mentalno zdravlje

857
00:46:27,080 --> 00:46:30,240
 i da ćemo sve preživjeti.

858
00:46:30,240 --> 00:46:36,500
 Slavice, misao za sve poduzetnice

859
00:46:36,500 --> 00:46:38,260
 i one koje će to tek postati.

860
00:46:38,260 --> 00:46:41,700
 Pa ja sam se susrela,

861
00:46:41,700 --> 00:46:44,700
 je s dosta žena što bi krenula u poduzetništvo.

862
00:46:44,700 --> 00:46:46,540
 Međutim, njihovi je nešto kočiti

863
00:46:46,540 --> 00:46:48,860
 kao što je, ma moram još završiti.

864
00:46:48,880 --> 00:46:51,600
 ovo, još ću, dakle djeca malo narastu,

865
00:46:51,600 --> 00:46:53,780
 nek sad završim još ovaj tečaj,

866
00:46:53,780 --> 00:46:56,860
 nek sad muž i nešto se sredi sa svojim poslom.

867
00:46:57,300 --> 00:46:59,180
 nemojte to raditi s sebi,

868
00:46:59,180 --> 00:47:01,620
 sve možete putem riješiti,

869
00:47:01,620 --> 00:47:03,460
 samo skočite i plivajte.

870
00:47:03,460 --> 00:47:05,720
 Ja mislim da je to jedno rješenje,

871
00:47:05,720 --> 00:47:06,620
 nemojte pre kasno.

872
00:47:06,620 --> 00:47:09,680
 Eto, meni je drago da sam joj ovako rano krenula.

873
00:47:12,320 --> 00:47:16,540
 super, super, super, plivajte i s mobitelom i bez mobitela.

874
00:47:16,540 --> 00:47:18,140
 Danira, da čujemo još tebe.

875
00:47:20,940 --> 00:47:24,560
 Ja stvarno smatram da žene poduzetnice treba podržati,

876
00:47:24,560 --> 00:47:26,980
 da treba imati razumijevanja za nas,

877
00:47:26,980 --> 00:47:30,460
 jer vjerujem da ženimo stvarno genijalne ideje,

878
00:47:30,460 --> 00:47:32,340
 genijalne inovacije,

879
00:47:32,340 --> 00:47:35,840
 koje vrlo često ostanu zatvorene u četiri zida

880
00:47:35,840 --> 00:47:37,340
 zbog toga što se boje krenuti

881
00:47:37,340 --> 00:47:39,320
 i zbog nerazumijevanja okoline.

882
00:47:39,320 --> 00:47:42,240
 Baš, da možemo biti i majke i žene

883
00:47:42,240 --> 00:47:43,720
 i domaćice i poduzetnice,

884
00:47:43,840 --> 00:47:44,400
 sve ujedno.

885
00:47:44,400 --> 00:47:47,740
 Samo nam treba malo podržke.

886
00:47:47,740 --> 00:47:48,600
 Tako je.

887
00:47:48,600 --> 00:47:49,260
 Pa evo,

888
00:47:49,260 --> 00:47:52,480
 upravo to, upravo to,

889
00:47:52,480 --> 00:47:55,620
 to je misao s kombiji tijela i završiti.

890
00:47:55,620 --> 00:47:58,820
 Hrabrite svoje prijateljice,

891
00:47:58,820 --> 00:48:02,160
 sestre, majke, čeri, žene

892
00:48:02,160 --> 00:48:06,800
 da se otisnu te poduzetničke vode.

893
00:48:06,800 --> 00:48:09,880
 Hrabrite im, ponavljajte da sve mogu,

894
00:48:09,880 --> 00:48:11,520
 jer to je doista tako.

895
00:48:11,520 --> 00:48:13,600
 A evo, već smo se i dotakli

896
00:48:13,600 --> 00:48:14,680
 i odgoja.

897
00:48:14,680 --> 00:48:16,620
 Stjepan je također spomenuo

898
00:48:16,620 --> 00:48:17,880
 da sve počinje od škole,

899
00:48:17,880 --> 00:48:20,700
 pa i odgajajte svoje kćeri

900
00:48:20,700 --> 00:48:23,520
 onako da mogu napraviti sve što žele

901
00:48:23,520 --> 00:48:26,960
 i postati apsolutno sve što žele biti.

902
00:48:26,960 --> 00:48:29,120
 Doista nema nikakvih ograničenja.

903
00:48:29,120 --> 00:48:31,680
 Pa evo, hvala vam svima

904
00:48:31,680 --> 00:48:33,740
 što ste nas gledali i slušali.

905
00:48:33,740 --> 00:48:37,100
 Hvala Ivani, Daniri, Slavici i Stjepanu

906
00:48:37,100 --> 00:48:40,640
 i do nekog sljedećeg trenutka,

907
00:48:40,640 --> 00:48:42,260
 do možda sljedećeg dana žena,

908
00:48:42,360 --> 00:48:43,920
 ali nadam se i prije da ćemo se

909
00:48:43,920 --> 00:48:45,400
 opet vidjeti na okupu.

910
00:48:45,400 --> 00:48:47,320
 Doviđenja.

911
00:48:47,320 --> 00:48:48,000
 Hvala vam.

912
00:48:48,000 --> 00:48:48,380
 Čao.

913
00:48:48,380 --> 00:48:49,660
 Čao.

